               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, made in the government scriptorium, belonging to Däjazmač Admasu Wäsän, including Angels Praise Her, ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ ለማርያም፡; Concluding Prayer and Concluding Table Prayer</summary>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="164r"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="164r" to="165r"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT3108RepCh388"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="165r" to="167v"/>
                    <title>A very elaborate Concluding Prayer for Praises of Mary, Gate of Light and Angels Praise Her</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <note>with an extensive list of relatives, living and dead, for whom intercessions are made</note>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="166rv" to="166rv"/>
                    <title>Concluding Table Prayer which is part of the daily prayer</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለወልድ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ይደልዎሙ፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
